  "description": "The refrigerator, which represents the Serie 4 line of the German company Bosch, belongs to the mid-range models. The unit received two cooling circuits for independent temperature control in each of the chambers. It also supports the Full No Frost automatic defrost system, which will simplify the operation of the device. The Bosch KGN39XI316 refrigerator has an external touch control that allows you to select the optimal temperature, activate quick freezing or cooling, etc. The useful volume of the model is 366 liters, of which: 87 liters is a freezer, 255 liters is a refrigerator compartment, and 24 liters is a VitaFresh zero chamber. There is also a separate humidity zone, which is suitable for storing vegetables and fruits. The freezer is able to freeze up to 14 kg of food per day, and also keep cold in case of problems with electricity for 16 hours. It is also worth noting the efficiency of the model (energy class A ++), the presence of a door closing indicator and an acceptable noise level in operation (up to 39 dB).",
